des: These are daily tidbits of information and wisdom that Emily has gleaned from her journey into and through the music industry. They're life experiences, as well as pieces of advice from other musicians to her along her journey. All should serve you as inspiration for your day!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
